title: NFL Week 14, Fantasy Football Playoff Advice (Football 12/06)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings to break down Week 14 from a fantasy perspective. The guys discuss the Jaguars-Titans game (2:30), the Emmanuel Sanders injury (5:30), whether Patrick Mahomes must start against the Ravens (13:00), how to handle the Steelers running back situation (17:00), whether to start Justin Wilson for the 49ers (20:00), whether to start your studs in the playoffs (23:30), what to do with the Chargers running back situation (25:30), how to handle Spencer Ware (28:15), whether Rashaad Penny is a stash (32:50), if Gus Edwards needs to start (34:15), what defenses to stream (35:30) and DFS plays.
